last_episode_to_air.name: What Happens In Cabo, Doesn’t Stay In Cabo
last_episode_to_air.overview: Larry's lover is no longer a mystery and their relationship is better than ever, until he gets blindsided by a confession.  Agu makes a last ditch effort with Kamani. Kamani forces Emily to face her demons.  After Larry treats his friends to an amazing day on a luxury yacht, they return the favor by surprising him with an unforgettable final night.

name: Invite Only Cabo
overview: When social connector Larry Sims invites six of his friends from different phases in his life on a luxury vacation in Cabo San Lucas, Mexico, no one knows what to expect, especially since most of his friends know next-to-nothing about the other guests.

episodes.name: Tick Tick Boom
episodes.overview: Sparks fly between Agu and Kamani. Emily shocks the group by removing something in a restaurant. Larry and Bianca share a steamy encounter.

episodes.name: Dancing With the Devil
episodes.overview: Scandal hits the vacation home following a night of partying in Cabo. Emily makes a life-altering decision. Kamani exposes Bianca's behavior to Larry.

episodes.name: Blame It on the Alcohol
episodes.overview: The crew lives the luxe Cabo life at a bottle popping pool party, but the sexy vibes vanish when Bianca asks Larry a jaw-dropping question. Jermane faces one of his greatest fears, while Agu tries to get back in Kamani's good graces, and for one of Larry's friends, a full-throttle ATV ride ends in disaster.

episodes.name: Secrets and Lies
episodes.overview: Once the dust settles from the ATV accident, Agu tries to get closer with Kamani, but Emily doesn't make it easy on him. For Bianca's birthday, Larry cooks up plans so big that the guys are forced to step in and intervene, leading Larry to drop a bomb that leaves everyone's heads spinning.

episodes.name: Dirty Little Secret
episodes.overview: Larry stuns everyone with a mystery guest, who comes into the house with guns blazing. The group gets their adrenaline fix by leaping head first into a Mexican canyon. And when Larry surprises Emily with her boyfriend for her birthday, it leaves her scrambling to keep her infidelity a secret.

episodes.name: Caught in the Act
episodes.overview: A sushi dinner gets messy when Kamani and Emily let their claws out. Larry and Bianca witness a backseat bombshell that they try to contain, but when the secret is finally revealed, emotions explode, and for one of Larry's friends, this vacation might be over.

episodes.name: Undercover Lover
episodes.overview: When Larry brings his secret lover to the house, Jermane leads an interrogation. A wild night of partying ends with an epic truth-telling explosion between Emily and Agu. Larry cracks under the pressure, leaving the entire vacation in limbo.
